==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Unactive
<hw>Un*ac"tive</hw>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Inactive; listless.</def>
<mark>[R.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>While other animals <qex>unactive</qex> range.</q>
<rj><qau>Milton.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Unactive</ent>⟦br⟧

==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Unactive
<hw>Un*ac"tive</hw>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <ety>[1st pref. <ets>un-</ets> +
<ets>active</ets>; or from <ets>unactive</ets>, a.]</ety> <def>To render
inactive or listless.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark>
